FBIS3-54411 "drnes017_r_94003" FBIS-NES-94-017 Document Type:Daily Report 26 Jan 1994 India Foiling Pakistani `Designs' on Kashmir Urged BK2501163494 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 25 Jan 94 BK2501163494 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The leader of the opposition in the Lok Sabha, Mr. Atal Behari Vajpayee, has said that the government should demonstrate its clarity of purpose and foil the evil designs of Pakistan on Jammu and Kashmir. In a statement in New Delhi today, the BJP [Bharatiya Janata Party] leader said Mrs. Bhutto's call for a Pakistan bundh [strike] on the fifth of next month cannot cover Kashmir as it is an integral part of India.
